mmer-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Concert-Hans-Zimmer-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Concert-Hans-Zimmer-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Legendary composer <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hans-zimmer">Hans Zimmer</a> will be coming to cinemas with a host of famous names in a concert film titled <em>Hans Zimmer &amp; Friends: Diamond In The Desert</em> .</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-greatest-hans-zimmer-scores-3457968">The greatest Hans Zimmer scores</a></strong></li></ul><p> The film features conversations with film luminaries such as <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">Christopher Nolan</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denis-villeneuve">Denis Villeneuve</a> ; movie stars <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timothee-chalamet">Timothée Chalamet</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zendaya">Zendaya</a> ; as well as music icons <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/johnny-marr">Johnny Marr</a> . It will screen in select cinemas across The Americas, Europe, Asia, and United Arab Emirates, with limited screenings beginning March 19.</p><p> A press release read: “Decades of cinematic masterpieces are brought to life by his band and a world-class orchestra at Dubai&#39;s iconic Coca-Cola Arena, the star-studded Al Wasl Plaza dome at Expo City Dubai and beyond. From the dunes of the Arabian Desert to the heights of Jumeirah Burj Al Arab, these performances deliver an intimate and unique experience of Zimmer&#39;s most beloved and renowned movie soundtracks”.</p><p> It is directed by Paul Dugdale, who has made concert films for <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a> , and will be executive produced by Jerry Bruckheimer, whom Zimmer worked with on numerous blockbusters including <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/top-gun"><em>Top Gun: Maverick</em></a> and the <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/pirates-of-the-carribean"><em>Pirates Of The Caribbean</em></a> films.</p><p> Tickets are on sale from Wednesday, February 5 at 9 am ET/2 pm GMT at <a href="https://trafalgarentertainment-26166210.hs-sites-eu1.com/hans-zimmer-friends-diamond-in-the-desert" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hanszimmerfilm.com</a> , along with all the screening locations.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> The news you&#39;ve ALL been waiting for <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> “Hans Zimmer &amp; Friends: Diamond in the Desert” is coming to select global cinemas beginning 19th March!</p><p> Tickets on sale on 5th February. Sign up for more information at <a href="https://t.co/R0Lzz01uwL">https://t.co/R0Lzz01uwL</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/HansZimmerFilm?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#HansZimmerFilm</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/HansZimmerLive?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#HansZimmerLive</a> <a href="https://t.co/c2C7gUpeqk">pic.twitter.com/c2C7gUpeqk</a></p><p> — Hans Zimmer Live (@HansZimmerLive) <a href="https://twitter.com/HansZimmerLive/status/1884617205121269819?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 29, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> In the release, Zimmer was quoted as saying: “ <em>The Hans Zimmer Live tour</em> has been one of the most exciting experiences of my career, and I&#39;m thrilled to bring it to an audience in cinemas globally with <em>Diamond in the Desert</em> .</p><p> “Seeing these compositions transform from their big-screen origins to the live show then back to the big screen is a delightful full-circle moment. I hope audiences enjoy this peek behind the curtain as much as we enjoyed making it”.</p><p> Winner of two <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">Academy Awards</a> , a <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/bafta">BAFTA Award</a> , and four <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">Grammys</a> , Zimmer is considered one of the great film composers. His music from the movies <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/dune">Dune</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-2">Gladiator</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/interstellar">Interstellar</a> ,</em> and <em>The Lion King</em> will be part of the film, which promises “a rare glimpse into Zimmer&#39;s creative process”.</p><p> Recently, Zimmer was revealed to be working on <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hans-zimmer-to-reimagine-saudi-arabias-national-anthem-3831818">a reimagined version of the Saudi Arabian national anthem, as one of several collaborations with the country.</a></p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hans-zimmer-friends-concert-film-coming-to-cinemas-3832965">&#39;Hans Zimmer &amp; Friends&#39; concert film coming to cinemas</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
